				<p>Thanks for responding, @patrix.  So the comments made by klanomath and grgarside are the result of the flagging **only** and not them flagging *and* commenting (which the wording makes it appear)?  I guess that's the source of my confusion, these comments don't appear when I flag a question.</p>
