				<p>I want to be consistent with the rest of the site.  I see value in letting the OP know, as soon as possible, the reason for the flag (because it can take hours for the question to close and the close-reason to appear).  I'm ok if you guys don't think that's a good way to proceed so I won't add those comments anymore.  Thanks for clearing that up for me!</p>
